	<h1 class="title">为你那微不足道的快乐，我送上意义深远的忧愁</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Laren Stover</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-11-13 19:00:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/17443/medium/17443.jpg?1447294261" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


